{"tid":348932,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[行路撚]799公里聖雅各朝聖之路","createTime":"2017-08-06T06:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T03:05:00.000Z","uid":2329,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fef49ce02dde79bf464c42345bdcd5caa7e0e30","tid":348932,"uid":2329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"2010年電影《The Way 朝聖之路》講一個中產醫生老豆個仔，放棄讀博士走左去旅行。臨走因為對生活既睇法唔同而同老豆鬧左交。過兩日老豆收到電話話佢個仔死左係西班牙，老豆飛去處理身後事知道佢開始行朝聖之路既時候出左意外，然後就決定帶埋個仔d 骨灰代佢行。由最初唔習慣到識左班fd 一齊上路，最後行到終點，將個仔d 骨灰撒落太平洋。幫個仔完成朝聖亦都幫自己完成左，開始了解個仔既想法重新了解生活。<br />\n呢條朝聖之路就係聖雅各之路。由法國南部St. jean pied de port 到西班牙北部Santiago，全長約799公里，徒步完成平均28-35日。<br />\n1993年被列入世界文化遺產，每年約有十萬人行。<br />\n完成後可獲教庭頒發證書，據講可以減半人世間所犯既罪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/144242_abf31f57f4cc59e17c17752b50afff58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F144242_abf31f57f4cc59e17c17752b50afff58.jpg&h=b2458ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/144248_b7dfc87b24dd4cc3862bd2dc59fc5df7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F144248_b7dfc87b24dd4cc3862bd2dc59fc5df7.jpg&h=a1b9c319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%81%96%E9%9B%85%E5%90%84%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2581%2596%25E9%259B%2585%25E5%2590%2584%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=G4MF%2FyElbYW45j5OCb%2FpFzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=12aad9eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%81%96%E9%9B%85%E5%90%84%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n平時坐office少運動又肥又無乜體力年紀又開始大既小弟，今年年初無啦啦決定要起行挑戰了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/145329_5af6c0e8f79a7495336a9fa29820bacc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F145329_5af6c0e8f79a7495336a9fa29820bacc.jpg&h=a4e63929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/145334_61dabb4996a4dad655372532746c3af9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F145334_61dabb4996a4dad655372532746c3af9.jpg&h=5ffb8749&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9683e063dda92eebcd42c52d75ea9447898b0220","tid":348932,"uid":2329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"朝聖前首先要去Pilgrim office 登記，除左起點外沿路都會有。放低兩歐有本朝聖passport、有疊地圖資料同一塊貝殼。Passport 用黎儲印仔記錄行程同埋入住庇護所*。貝殼係屬於朝聖者既聖物，每個人都會掛一塊係身。而幾百個今日出發既人之中，只有一個痴線佬係香港人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/150022_d32ddeb6acae135f6131cc77a21fd20b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F150022_d32ddeb6acae135f6131cc77a21fd20b.jpg&h=897a9a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/150027_b476d56e11f9f61c991e487e672a8469.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F150027_b476d56e11f9f61c991e487e672a8469.jpg&h=41ddc9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/150035_c1fc3308db30b91988ba9a229d9aa747.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F150035_c1fc3308db30b91988ba9a229d9aa747.jpg&h=5a3405ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dadafe927ded158190fbfd6892a8332494d66c0e","tid":348932,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T07:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7bd9bb0f1ac5591eaa433c9be81e74c10a3c84","tid":348932,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"痴線佬POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3c9ec6c3e7e634c6b14f5f19e7266d87403817","tid":348932,"uid":2329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b753602e4c0fc29bb0e6b4068e25c7d45bd792","tid":348932,"uid":89709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"355f1a79ef782f0cdf546c72fcb52191002e5ec5","tid":348932,"uid":133353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"6月先係摩洛哥識左個韓妹佢都係徒步行朝聖之路"},{"pid":"f426e56195e112137fbfd3b343b38e464bc80c6e","tid":348932,"uid":2329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6月先係摩洛哥識左個韓妹佢都係徒步行朝聖之路</blockquote><br />\n勁多韓妹行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da78f4a005fdf593161cf41ca915d8b608d761d","tid":348932,"uid":8138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7f09516c649828d5b568fd7aab3e3506a54bcb","tid":348932,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"徒步L留名<br />\n<br />\n朝聖之路太熱門所以唔想去行"},{"pid":"11a5dad5ba8d2b3bc8cfd37d6bd360d2502b3e63","tid":348932,"uid":121347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"786351fe4c9c654baf644cb