">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%81%96%E9%9B%85%E5%90%84%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n平時坐office少運動又肥又無乜體力年紀又開始大既小弟，今年年初無啦啦決定要起行挑戰了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/145329_5af6c0e8f79a7495336a9fa29820bacc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F145329_5af6c0e8f79a7495336a9fa29820bacc.jpg&h=a4e63929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/145334_61dabb4996a4dad655372532746c3af9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F145334_61dabb4996a4dad655372532746c3af9.jpg&h=5ffb8749&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n強帖留名"},{"pid":"7ebcfbb8920cd6dbeebd57896a5547651b57cfd5","tid":348932,"uid":126502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗緊9月去, 但好驚換唔到機票, 想問坐到去邊個城市之後再去呢個起點先可以開始行最方便?<br />\n<br />\n另外樓主行左幾多日? 我預只有4星期, 諗緊可以開頭行過左過山之後坐番100-200公里的車再開始行會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為無時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四星期如果你有心行,其實係行到<br />\n上年識個slovenia fd 23日行到santiago<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想坐車,可以係burgos 坐車,坐到邊就自已睇ALSA 個apps再算"},{"pid":"4e02823779735ac6cee81d5c00feff1578ac0433","tid":348932,"uid":98186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b987ef74cb25611ac06dd2e50c00a3d31df24e03","tid":348932,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"繼東海道又一痴線佬Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名支持"},{"pid":"3995cfe7d882e20cd7d47e019ad3f562433f370d","tid":348932,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"留名贖罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602a1dd9a337b840571936a0feb37559d8febd4e","tid":348932,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ee9720fb71c5a8119d96fe1f7597e1d82f2c5d","tid":348932,"uid":121347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"112182babd1fca689a9a1dd0a7ddfcd4dcf0de81","tid":348932,"uid":36817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"ddd72645eacb81e3ad35ee806113e383d3d9bce7","tid":348932,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"樓主係而家開始定行完左？<br />\n<br />\nAny 肥，加油，一路平安！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14bff49829a84af66ec18a49aed7a04adf9f019","tid":348932,"uid":121347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19deee1a84b4bdd67dd562c1ce2183d705f55518","tid":348932,"uid":126502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我諗緊9月去, 但好驚換唔到機票, 想問坐到去邊個城市之後再去呢個起點先可以開始行最方便?<br />\n<br />\n另外樓主行左幾多日? 我預只有4星期, 諗緊可以開頭行過左過山之後坐番100-200公里的車再開始行會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為無時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四星期如果你有心行,其實係行到<br />\n上年識個slovenia fd 23日行到santiago<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想坐車,可以係burgos 坐車,坐到邊就自已睇ALSA 個apps再算</blockquote><br />\n得9月8日定10日先到西班牙, 仲打算留一日再佳多轉內陸機飛去最近條線的城市, 所以應該11-12號先到步開始行, 所以無計, 因為我預5-6號左右要離開.[因要坐一程機聖地牙哥番馬德里, 再隔24小時先可以坐去英國轉機香港/ 里數機票問題.]<br />\n<br />\n咁我仲諗住要去埋個海邊.[當然坐車算....]<br />\n<br />\n同想係聖地牙哥留1-2日, 所以惟有中間去, 因為我家下番果份番一世, 一日都唔遲得, 遲一日番工會出EMAIL通知全世界呀邊個邊個拎急假去左旅行.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[機票應隨時可改, 都係比小小里數出來, 反正我打算換頭等/.]</blockquote><br />\n仲心大心細諗緊好唔好行成程, 因為老實講如果日行50分里其實都OK, 但D朋友講難度太大.<br />\n<br />\n我CHECK過我背包好輕, 真係剩係, 拎個60L袋, 頂多裝3-4KG左右野.</blockquote><br />\n有無tg 你有咩問題可以直接問我<br />\n應該可以幫你well plan返個行程"}]}